column1: # yield        : yield (raw counts integrated over Pm) with all data-analysis cuts applied
# yield_eff    : yield corrected for inefficiencies (hms/shms tracking + live_time + proton absorption)
# yield_corr   : yield_eff corrected for external/internal impurities if any

column2: yield_rad / yield_norad (to be applied when calculating ratios)

column1: # sigma_raw_per_nucleon   : corrected yield (yield_corr) normalized by (total_charge|transpacency|area_density(g/cm2) (per nucleon))
# sigma_raw_per_proton    : corrected yield (yield_corr) normalized by (total_charge|transpacency|area_density (per proton) e.g. xA/Z )
# sigma_raw_per_nucleus   : corrected yield (yield_corr) normalized by (total_charge|transpacency|area_density (per nucleus) e.g xA )
# stat_rel_err            : relative statistical error on the total yield calculated as sqrt(yield)/yield
# norm_syst_rel_err       : relative systematic error due to normalization correction factors (hms/shms track efficiencies
# T N Z A                 : transparency (T) # of neutrons (N) protons(Z) and nucleons (A)
